ACCEPT_VERSIONS

static final String ACCEPT_VERSIONS
The name of the OGC Web Service Common (OWS) AcceptVersions parameter. The associated value must be a prioritized sequence of one or more versions accepted by the client, with preferred versions listed first. Versions are comma delimited and formatted as x.y.z, where x, y and z are integers in the range 0-99.

Used by WFS versions 1.1.0 and 2.0.0. Not used by WFS version 1.0.0, WMS version 1.1.1, and WMS version 1.3.0.
